\large \int_0^{x_0}\frac{y_0}{1+\frac{(1-a)x}{a(x_0-x)}}dx.
y_0x_0\int_0^1\frac{a(1-u)}{a+(1-2a)u}du.
\frac{a(1-u)}{a+(1-2a)u}=\frac{A}{a+(1-2a)u}+B.
\begin{cases}A+aB=a \\ B(1-2a)=-a\end{cases}
B=\frac{a}{2a-1};\quad A=\frac{a(a-1)}{2a-1}.
